  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fund a teacher and teach a class in Latin America</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A good teacher can be one of the most inspiring people. Here at Fly the Phoenix we are very aware of this and only employ the best local teachers who have trained well and are really passionate about their work. Schools often fail in Latin America because the teachers are of low quality.  Due to COVID-19 we aim to provide hand sanitizer and supplies of soap over the long-term for all our students for when they enter and leave the schools each day to reassure parents that it is a safe environment</narrative>
  </description>
